-- Croatia Seeks Advisers for Sale of Croatia Osiguranje, HPB
-- B y   J a s m i n a   K u z m a n o v i c
-- 2012-09-19T15:11:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-19/croatia-seeks-advisers-for-sale-of-croatia-osiguranje-hpb.html
Croatia ’s  Finance Ministry 
published a tender seeking advisers for the sale of  Croatia
Osiguranje d.d. , the country’s largest insurer, and  Hrvatska
Postanska Banka d.d. , the last major state-owned bank.  Offers will be opened on Oct. 29 and Oct. 30 for HPB and
Croatia Osiguranje, respectively, the ministry said today in a
statement on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jasmina Kuzmanovic in Zagreb at 
